Just like I said to Kenshiiro – if you could kill the mobs being left up, i.e. the 3rd and 4th Ancients, you would already be on rotation.  No one kills the last two and leaves the front two up – indeed, I would be impressed if they could, right before I petitioned them for exploiting.  You deciding on your own, to go down and snipe mobs that you aren’t on rotation for is as bad as guilds that did the same to Ikky and Eashen in the N ToV days.  Additionally, the Ancients guilds go down the day after the ST rotation guild, they don’t go down midweek like you seem to want free reign to do for the non-Ancients guilds.  Sorry, that’s not fair to the up and coming ST guilds who want their shots at the Ancients and aren’t up on a patch day.<br>
